data.description: Discover this elegant Lake Brenda gem, nestled on a hillside lot boasting picturesque lake views and surrounded by a lush canopy of mature trees. This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home includes a sunroom that can effortlessly transform into a flexible space or home office. Step into the expansive living room with tall ceilings that complements the wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The dining area is accentuated by floor-to-ceiling windows that offer breathtaking views and bathe the space in natural light. The well-appointed galley kitchen is equipped with a pantry, stylish tile countertops, and a charming window overlooking the sunroom. The fenced backyard serves as a private oasis, featuring an inviting in-ground pool, a pool house complete with a bathroom and storage space, and an impressive workshop. Experience the tranquil lifestyle of this Lake Brenda masterpiece, where modern living meets natural beauty.
